    `production/specs/code-mapping.md` documents how each incubation component maps to production:


    ┌───────────────────────────┬───────────────────────────────┬──────────────────────────────────────────┐
    │ Incubation Component      │ Production Location           │ Key Changes                              │
    ├───────────────────────────┼───────────────────────────────┼──────────────────────────────────────────┤
    │ src/agent/core_loop.py    │ agent/customer_success_agent.py │ Convert to OpenAI Agents SDK             │
    │ src/agent/memory_agent.py │ agent/customer_success_agent.py │ Merge logic, add SDK decorators          │
    │ src/tools/mcp_server.py   │ agent/tools.py                │ @server.tool → @function_tool + Pydantic │
    │ (spec only)               │ channels/gmail_handler.py     │ Implement Gmail API                      │
    │ (spec only)               │ channels/whatsapp_handler.py  │ Implement Twilio WhatsApp                │
    │ (spec only)               │ channels/web_form_handler.py    │ Implement FastAPI + React                │
    │ (new)                     │ workers/message_processor.py  │ Kafka consumer + agent                   │
    │ (new)                     │ api/main.py                   │ FastAPI with webhooks                    │
    └───────────────────────────┴───────────────────────────────┴──────────────────────────────────────────┘


    Key Transition Changes

     1. Tool Decorator: @server.tool → @function_tool with Pydantic BaseModel
     2. Storage: In-memory dicts → PostgreSQL with asyncpg
     3. Logging: print() → logging module with structured logs
     4. Config: Hardcoded values → Environment variables + ConfigMaps


