    Key Differences from MCP (Incubation)


    ┌──────────────────┬─────────────────────┬────────────────────────────────────────────┐
    │ Aspect           │ MCP (Incubation)    │ OpenAI SDK (Production)                    │
    ├──────────────────┼─────────────────────┼────────────────────────────────────────────┤
    │ Decorator        │ @server.tool        │ @function_tool                             │
    │ Input Validation │ Loose string params │ Pydantic BaseModel with Field constraints  │
    │ Error Handling   │ Basic try/catch     │ Comprehensive with graceful fallbacks      │
    │ Docstrings       │ Basic               │ Detailed with examples, constraints, TODOs │
    │ Type Hints       │ Basic               │ Full typing with Optional, List, Dict      │
    │ Logging          │ Print statements    │ Structured logging with context            │
    │ Database         │ In-memory dicts     │ Prepared for asyncpg + PostgreSQL          │
    └──────────────────┴─────────────────────┴────────────────────────────────────────────┘

