    ---

    Production-Ready Features

    1. Explicit Workflow Ordering:

     1 1st: Create Ticket (ALWAYS FIRST)
     2 2nd: Get Customer History
     3 3rd: Search Knowledge Base (If Product Question)
     4 4th: Analyze Sentiment (On Every Message)
     5 5th: Escalate to Human (If Triggers Detected)
     6 6th: Send Response (ALWAYS LAST - NEVER SKIP)

    2. Quantified Constraints:
     - Email: Up to 500 words
     - WhatsApp: Under 300 characters (preferably 160)
     - Web Form: Up to 300 words
     - Sentiment threshold: < 0.3 = escalate
     - Response times: Critical=1h, High=4h, Normal=24h

    3. Exact Keyword Lists:

     1 Pricing: "price", "cost", "discount", "enterprise pricing", "upgrade cost", "how much", "billing"
     2 Refund: "refund", "chargeback", "money back", "double charged", "overcharged"
     3 Security: "hacked", "unauthorized access", "data breach", "account compromised"
     4 Legal: "lawyer", "attorney", "sue", "lawsuit", "legal action", "GDPR", "subpoena"

    4. Complete Response Templates:
     - Email template with greeting, body, signature, ticket reference
     - WhatsApp template with truncation guidance and emoji
     - Web form template with documentation link

    5. Error Handling Guidance:
     - Tool failure handling
     - Knowledge base unavailable response
     - Very angry customer protocol (sentiment < 0.2)

    ---

    Additional Templates Included

    Channel Response Templates:
     - EMAIL_RESPONSE_TEMPLATE
     - WHATSAPP_RESPONSE_TEMPLATE
     - WEB_FORM_RESPONSE_TEMPLATE

    Escalation Response Templates:
     - ESCALATION_RESPONSES dict with 8 escalation types

    Greeting Templates:
     - EMAIL_GREETINGS (3 options)
     - WHATSAPP_GREETINGS (4 options)
     - WEB_FORM_GREETINGS (3 options)

    Signature Templates:
     - EMAIL_SIGNATURE (full contact info)
     - WHATSAPP_SIGNATURE (emoji + CTA)
     - WEB_FORM_SIGNATURE (docs link)

    Helper Prompts:
     - TOOL_ORDER_REMINDER - 6-step workflow reminder
     - CONTINUATION_PROMPT - For returning customers
     - RETURNING_CUSTOMER_PROMPT - History awareness
     - RESPONSE_QUALITY_CHECKLIST - 12-point verification

